-	Email Remittance Advice - New bulk email functionality for sending remittance advice documents to vendors
o	Send one email per reconciliation with PDF attachment
o	Optional "Combine Per Vendor" mode sends one email with multiple PDF attachments
o	Uses per-vendor email configuration from Document Layouts
o	Falls back to Vendor Card email if not configured
o	Preview option to review emails before sending
o	Only “Archived” reconciliation are included.

-	Custom Email Body Support - Configure Word layouts for email body content
o	Supports both modern platform layouts and legacy custom layouts
o	Falls back to professional HTML table format

-	Validation Before Send - All records validated before processing begins
o	Missing email addresses reported all at once
o	Prevents partial sends

-	Date Range Filtering - Filter reconciliations by Statement Date
o	End Date is mandatory
o	Start Date is optional

Technical Improvements

-	8 integration events for extensibility
-	Compatible with BC standard layout selection patterns
-	Inline CSS for cross-email-client compatibility
-	AppSource ready (OnPrem and SaaS)

Prerequisites

-	Email Account must be configured in Business Central
-	Vendors should have email addresses configured (Vendor Card or Document Layouts)

